title: Watch Tom Brady transform into 'Psycho Tom' before Super Bowl LI
text:
Feb 5, 2017 at 6:11p ET 0Shares 
Tom Brady rarely contains his intensity before a big game. Skip Bayless has said it’s Brady’s rage and intensity that sets him apart, and earns him the nickname “Psycho Tom.” With a record fifth Super Bowl ring in sight, it’s no surprise to see the New England Patriots star raring to go. 
As he jogged with fellow Patriots quarterbacks Jimmy Garoppolo and Jacoby Brissett before the start of Sunday’s game, Brady shouted and threw a hellacious fist pump.
